.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.prod
.env.production
.env.staging
# Committed on purpose: deterministic, secret-free production build inputs.
# Vite bakes VITE_* vars into the client bundle, so they are public by
# definition (visible in any built asset / DevTools) and are NOT secrets.
# Required so the deploy-web workflow builds against the AWS prod API from a
# clean CI checkout instead of falling back to localhost.
!.env.production
